<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3745.1.5>
    dc:creator "Zonstein, Sergei L.; Marusik, Yuri M.; Koponen, Seppo" ;
    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "Redescription of three species of Filistatidae (Araneae) described by C. F. Roewer from Afghanistan" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222733>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222735> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222733>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 15. Female copulatory organs of Pholcoides afghana (11 – 12), Zaitunia afghana (13) and Tricalamus lindbergi (14 - 15). 11, 13 ventral; 12, 14 – 15 dorsal. Abbreviations: Ar accessorial receptacle; Mr main receptacle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222735>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 27. Somatic characters and female copulatory organ of paratype of Zaitunia afghana. 21 – 22, 24 body, dorsal, ventral and lateral, respectively; 23 prosoma, dorsal; 25 metatarsus IV showing calamistrum; 26 – 27 copulatory organ, 26 ventral and 27 dorso-anterior." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

